@node INTRO "1 Introduction and Concepts"
@next INSTALL
Welcome to KingFisher!

If you are a registered user of KingFisher, I thank you for your support (now and anytime you read this again ;-) If you have @{b}not yet registered@{ub}, please read section @{" 1.1 " link WHYREGISTER} to find out why you really should consider registering the software.

1.1	@{" Why Register? " link WHYREGISTER}
1.2	@{" What is KingFisher? " link WHATISKF}
1.3	@{" What does KingFisher consist of? " link COMPONENTS}
1.4	@{" How does KingFisher work? " link WORKHOW}

1.5	@{" Why 'KingFisher'?!? " link WHYKF}
