@{b}Jure Vrhovnik@{ub}
	@{lindent 8}For his link library routines (with source) to recolor images (see dev/c/SupraLib.lha on @{" Aminet " link AMINET}.)@{lindent 0}

@{b}Jochen Wiedmann@{ub}
