I also extend my gratitude to the efforts of my @{" Translators " link TRANSLATORS} by whose efforts you can (hopefully) enjoy KingFisher in your native language.

And not to forget, those who have sent in bug reports detailed enough to help me locate and fix various problems over the years.

@{b}And last, but not least, my thanks to you who have registered KingFisher and shown your very real support for my efforts. You know who you are. Cheers!@{ub}
